---
description: Fast deterministic units—pure logic, AAA, one behavior per test
alwaysApply: false
---

# Unit tests

- **AAA** per case; one behavior per test. Name: `<unit> <behavior> when <condition>` (or framework style).
- Pure: no real net/DB/fs—mock boundaries you don’t own, never the unit under test.
- Happy + boundary + error paths. No flaky time/random/order deps.
